<title>USA: National Patent arranges $25 mln credit.</title>
<headline>National Patent arranges $25 mln credit.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>National Patent Development Corp said on Tuesday that it and certain wholly owned subsidiaries entered into a three-year, $25 million revolving credit agreement with a syndicate of three banks.</p>
<p>The agreement replaces other loan arrangements currently in place, the company said.</p>
<p>National Patent supplies various support services to companies and government entities.</p>
